E-MailRelay windows build
=========================

cmake
-----
Cmake 2.8.12.1 source code with a "build" directory 
created by running 

	cd build && cmake -G 'NMake Makefiles' ..

using cmake 3.17.

Build on windows without "nmake" with:

	cd cmake\build
	..\..\makecmake.bat
	PATH=<cwd>\cmake\build;%PATH%

Or with a full MSVC installation:

	cd cmake\build
	nmake cmake

perl
----
Perl 5.38.0 source code.


qt5
---
Qt source code.

Build on windows with:

	cd qt5
	perl ../emailrelay/libexec/qtbuild.pl


emailrelay
----------
E-MailRelay source.

Build on windows with:

	cd emailrelay
	perl winbuild.pl

